{"word":"H1523 - גִּיל - gîyl - gheel - Be glad","slug":"H1523","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">גִּיל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>gîyl"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>gheel"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Be glad"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D5;&#x05BC;&#x05DC;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&#x05D2;&#x05BC;&#x05D9;&#x05DC; - <a href='S:g'>g</a>&#x0131;&#x0302;yl  gu&#x0302;l</b> - <i>gheel, gool</i><p/>A primitive root; properly to <i>spin</i> around (under the influence of any violent emotion), that is, usually <i>rejoice</i>, or (as <i>cringing</i>) <i>fear: - </i>be glad, joy, be joyful, rejoice."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1524\">H1524</a>, <a href=\"#/H1525\">H1525</a>, <a href=\"#/H1526\">H1526</a>, <a href=\"#/H1542\">H1542</a>"}]}